                <note rend="inline" type="source">853.116/114: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Portugal (<persName type="from"
                            >South</persName>) to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Lisbon</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-01-04T12:00:00+00:00"
                            >January 4, 1933—noon</date>.<lb/>[Received January 4—11:10
                        a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1. My despatch No. 718, of September 29. Reductions in discriminatory duties of 2
                    and 4 percent, respectively, conceded by decree of January 2nd, effective that
                    day.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">South</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
